Call number browse in catalog-alma does not always display the location

comments.body: **Example from my local dev 'alma'** It seems that it misses the library name. **Example from catalog production**

The reason is that in the past with voyager we were including in the holdings_1display['location'] both the library and the location name. With alma because of the different grouping of libraries and locations, in the holdings_1display['location'] we include only the location and we don't include the library name.
